{"tid":1383349,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《急》一封email 幫幫 發起公務員82集會 顏武周","createTime":"2019-07-29T16:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T03:07:58.000Z","uid":282242,"like":76,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"f2f7d02bbb63adb6fbed0b06c96f518681917efb","tid":1383349,"uid":282242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:21:18.000Z","msg":"請大家幫幫手<br />\n堆公務員係電視出唒樣去申請不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nLwurnn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnLwurnn.png&h=348965ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家幫幫手<br />\n發起公務員集會嘅顏武周<br />\n有大量藍屍打1823投訴佢請幫忙send email比勞工處處長，對沖返投訴<br />\n<br />\nTo: cl_office@labour.gov.hk<br />\ncc: scsoffice@csb.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n致：<br />\n勞工處處長<br />\n陳嘉信先生, JP <br />\n<br />\n陳處長：<br />\n<br />\n本人得悉貴處二級助理勞工事務主任顏武周先生現正申請舉辦名為「公僕仝人，與民同行」的集會。近月，《逃犯條例》修訂爭議觸發香港多次大規模遊行示威，再加上警方處理方法亦引起廣泛關注及爭議，社會嚴重撕裂及對立。社會各界近日紛紛以聯署形式積極表達聲音，不少公務員亦加入行列。身為公僕一員的顏先生表示希望將這些聲音化作行動，向市民傳達公務員團隊聆聽到他們的聲音，願意告知政府，從而修補政府與市民之間的關係。本人十分欣賞顏先生的勇氣，願意承擔申辦集會此重任；同時非常支持顏先生的行動，讓公務員有機會在公餘時間表達對社會狀況的意見，對維護香港核心價值有莫大幫助。<br />\n<br />\n《基本法》第二十七條列明：「香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版的自由，結社、集會、遊行、示威的自由，組織和參加工會、罷工的權利和自由。」公務員作為香港居民一分子，應同樣享有這些權利，不應被侵犯。<br />\n<br />\n此外，《基本法》第三十九條又指出：「《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》、《經濟、社會與文化權利的國際公約》和國際勞工公約適用於香港的有關規定繼續有效，通過香港特別行政區的法律予以實施。」其中適用於香港特別行政區的國際勞工公約，包括《結社自由與保護組織權利公約》(87號)及《(公務員)勞動關係公約》(151號)。其中，後者明確提及公務員享有跟其他工人一樣的公民及政治權利，可以自由結社；而公務員工會則享有完全獨立於政府機構，不受後者干預的權利。<br />\n<br />\n本人認為，公務員透過組織或參與工會表達對於社會及政治事務的意見，甚至參與相關的活動或行動，理應受到充份的保護。因此，本人再次強調，本人絕對支持顏先生舉辦的集會，亦懇請貴處協助捍衛公務員在非執行公務時表達意見的權利。<br />\n<br />\n本人希望貴處回覆，假如顏先生或貴處其他同事因此事而遭無理投訴，貴處將如何處理。謝謝。<br />\n<br />\n市民<br />\nXXX<br />\n<br />\n副本送：<br />\n公務員事務局局長羅智光 先生, GBS, JP"},{"pid":"114eb3de1f81038d117841bfa493e29d176b5fae","tid":1383349,"uid":282242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:22:46.000Z","msg":"自推希望多d人見到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n難得公務員都加入！"},{"pid":"58bb78f35a7f82cd1b62a87626255dacc676366e","tid":1383349,"uid":282242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:23:04.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"90ebac5af825c25390d9c6ddde34ddfbfc9b613e","tid":1383349,"uid":282242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:23:19.000Z","msg":"三推"},{"pid":"534cfa40e8bac5154416357f3ec212a2af681b4a","tid":1383349,"uid":282242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:24:35.000Z","msg":"四<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6f62e75a5dbcedeef3de5200a71d839f57c1ab","tid":1383349,"uid":282242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:24:56.000Z","msg":"五<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五"},{"pid":"811405c4e1191e4c7ac59d44cd24aec459046026","tid":1383349,"uid":282242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:25:12.000Z","msg":"六<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />六"},{"pid":"a7539f8a249abd8ea5eed37e534c0ebbab1f54d5","tid":1383349,"uid":282242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:25:24.000Z","msg":"七<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a7be5e86e936442663fd875aa6ec923f82c042","tid":1383349,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:25:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5f9de0094274584c9cc29684512282a0994cbf6f","tid":1383349,"uid":282242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:25:40.000Z","msg":"八<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac39148975d36c94707e156e5200eeca05e406be","tid":1383349,"uid":282242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:26:00.000Z","msg":"九<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d6ad7e7c0344a3316fc0620b08b9b713de8577","tid":1383349,"uid":282242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:26:12.000Z","msg":"十！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a02170ed29866ebca2d51473b4748ff88430186","tid":1383349,"uid":184952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:26:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3f5ea11f2c63aee5bfeabc430ea3179322cebcd","tid":1383349,"uid":184952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:27:21.000Z","msg":"大家一齊send email"},{"pid":"3dedb9b25c1d289b70a52651ab3487a999d0d2ed","tid":1383349,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:28:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n2047到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭"},{"pid":"63f8283b906b84a1ffb2535ed2eb506e7a930089","tid":1383349,"uid":263668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:28:14.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"8b716ed22ea87e827c43200fe3522471b7393f56","tid":1383349,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:29:20.000Z","msg":"一定要撐，公務員做到呢步，都唔幫手，真係唔知點行落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea76cd9fe8d7a20461ea1766135e6454118d689","tid":1383349,"uid":281467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:30:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75190d60fd04b826cb9b65ce762ac8e83e04c0e8","tid":1383349,"uid":37986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:30:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0bcd832dd0904733a8a8ac49db96c24b90ec2404","tid":1383349,"uid":229296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:31:19.000Z","msg":"已sd，推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71461c4d012f8c2bea0e30ddade756f58d39829b","tid":1383349,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:31:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af7846a904d3bb9a87fe577ee5347b81dc2483d0","tid":1383349,"uid":281467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:36:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"34548dac113a4b154854aa68a5c94e98c2c07296","tid":1383349,"uid":281467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:39:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1030c7caf3bf41fe162db4c80f